description:
Emit structured registry.json with full identity expansions.

## Output Structure
{
  'commodities': [
    {
      'id': 'C:ELC',
      'kind': 'TRADABLE',
      'code': 'ELC',
      'key': 'electricity',
      'context': null,
      'tags': {...}
    },
    {
      'id': 'S:RSD:RES.ALL',
      'kind': 'SERVICE',
      'code': 'RSD',
      'key': 'residential_final_energy',
      'context': 'RES.ALL',
      'tags': {...}
    }
  ],
  'processes': [
    {
      'id': 'P:CCG:GEN:NEM_EAST',
      'parsed': {
