## Features
- Full abbreviation expansion (code → key)
- All Class A and Class B tags included
- Parsed ID components for tooling consumption

## Acceptance
- registry.json emitted alongside VEDA tables
- Round-trip: registry contains enough info to reconstruct VedaLang
- JSON schema validates output structure
